title: GOOD OMENS Official Trailer #2 (2019) David Tennant, Michael Sheen Fantasy Series HD
author: FTZ
comment:
Everyone: "There doesn't have to be a war."
America: "Of course there does, otherwise, how would we win it?"

In the good Omens fandom we don’t say "I love you"

We say "Get thee behind me foul fiend" and I think that’s beautiful.

“We have nothing whatsoever in common i don’t even like you!”

“You dooo!”
Love how the three horsemen look like people but Death is just an actual skeleton on a bike.
